WikiParser

Version 1.1

Copyright 2011, Fabian GraÃŸl

derived from
Copyright 2005, Steve Blinch
http://code.blitzaffe.com
http://code.blitzaffe.com/pages/phpclasses/files/wiki_parser_52-13

This class translates wiki formatting into HTML.


EXAMPLE

require_once(dirname(__FILE__).'/lib/WikiParser.class.php');

$parser = new WikiParser();

$text = "== Character formatting ==
This is ''emphasized'', this is '''really emphasized''', this is ''''grossly emphasized'''',
and this is just '''''freeking insane'''''.";

echo $parser->parse($text);


